parameters.name: SharedWith
parameters.description: The Amazon Web Services account ID, organization ID, or organizational unit (OU) ID with which the workload, lens, profile, or review template is shared.

parameters.name: ClientRequestToken
parameters.description: A unique case-sensitive string used to ensure that this request is idempotent (executes only once). You should not reuse the same token for other requests. If you retry a request with the same client request token and the same parameters after the original request has completed successfully, the result of the original request is returned. This field is autopopulated if not provided.

nested_items.name: ShareId
nested_items.description: The ID associated with the share.
